# Autopus-ADK Status Dashboard Demo
# Usage: cd demo && vhs status.tape

Output status.gif

Require auto

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1400
Set Height 800
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set CursorBlink true

Type "auto status"
Enter
Sleep 6s
